      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and <strong>mayo</strong> to a small bowl</p><p>Zest your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely grate (or chop) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>lime</strong> <strong>zest</strong> and a generous pinch of both <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to the yoghurt – this is your <strong>lime & garlic yoghurt</strong></p>",
